    $$
    \frac{S(x)}{x}=\sum_{n=1}^{\infty}(-1)^{n-1}(n+1)nx^{n-1}=\frac{\mathrm{d}^{2} }{\mathrm{d}x^{2} }\sum_{n=1}^{\infty}(-x)^{n+1}=\frac{\mathrm{d}^{2} }{\mathrm{d}x}\frac{1}{1+x}
